{"title":"最难忘……","authors":["魏沫"],"dates":[{"year":1962,"month":9,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"最难忘……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"魏沫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最难忘的是那一天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他来到了我们车间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炉火正红，笑容满面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掌声把马达声吞咽……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是麦穗黄的时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他来到了我们山沟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走遍公社，头戴草帽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一双又大又暖的手……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没想到就在这舰上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他看我们操炮练枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪花四溅，海鸥飞翔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他微笑着指点前方……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文艺园地里的幼苗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也受到阳光的照耀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他走上舞台，一一握手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一刻永生忘不了……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记忆力弱，记忆力强；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的记得，有的遗忘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唯有这事铭刻我心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲爱的领袖，亲爱的党！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}